# FAMM Design System — AI Rules

You are editing the FAMM fitness app. The design system is the contract.
Source of truth: `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`.

## Hard rules (lint will fail your PR if you break these)

1. No raw color literals. No `#abcdef`, no `rgb(...)`, no `hsl(...)`.
2. No raw pixel literals. No `16px`, no `padding: 12`, no magic numbers.
3. No inline `style={{ ... }}` on JSX outside `packages/ui/src/components/primitives/**`.
4. No new component library or icon set. We use `@famm/ui` + `lucide-react`.

## Reuse before you create

Before writing any new component:

1. Search `packages/ui/src/components/primitives` and
   `packages/ui/src/components/patterns` for an existing match.
2. If close-but-not-quite, extend the existing variant (cva) — do not fork.
3. If genuinely new:
   - Cross-feature reuse → propose as L2 pattern in `packages/ui/...patterns/`.
   - Feature-specific → place in `apps/web/src/components/<feature>/` as L3.
   - New atomic primitive → STOP. Ask the user before adding to L1.

## Tokens and styling

Use Tailwind classes backed by semantic tokens. Allowed families:

- Colors: `surface{-raised,-sunken,-overlay}`, `text-{primary,secondary,muted,inverse,onAccent}`,
  `accent{,-hover,-subtle}`, `signal-{success,danger,warning,pr}`,
  `border{,-subtle,-strong}`.
- Spacing: `p-inset-{xs,sm,md,lg,xl}`, `gap-stack-{xs..xl}`, `gap-inline-{xs..lg}`.
- Radius: `rounded-control`, `rounded-card`, `rounded-pill`.
- Shadow: `shadow-sm`, `shadow`, `shadow-lg`, `shadow-focus`.
- Motion: `duration-fast|base|slow`, `ease-standard|emphasized`.
- Type: `font-sans`, `font-mono`.

If the token you need doesn't exist, add it in `packages/ui/src/tokens/tokens.json`
and surface it in `packages/ui/tailwind.config.ts` in the same change.
Mention the new token in the PR description.

## Accessibility (always)

- Interactive elements need a visible focus ring (default is the `ring-DEFAULT` color).
- Touch targets ≥ 44×44 on touch viewports.
- Every form input gets a `<label>` (or the `FormField` pattern once it lands).
- Icons that convey meaning carry `aria-label`; decorative icons get `aria-hidden`.
- Animations over 200ms or involving translation must branch on
  `useReducedMotion()` from `@famm/ui`.

## Responsive

- Mobile-first. Default styles target `<sm`; add breakpoints upward (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`).
- Use layout primitives (`Stack`, `Cluster`, `Grid` when they exist) rather than
  bespoke media queries inside feature components.

## When unsure

Stop and ask. Do not guess between two valid patterns. Do not invent a
token name, color value, or component name.
